{
  "texts": [
    "We found no improvement to the performance of the LLMs, as Google already uses machine learning methods to identify the most important information to include in the preview.",
    "We equip the agent with the ability to query Google by leveraging the Reasoning and Acting (ReAct) framework, proposed by Yao et al. (2023), which allows an LLM to interact with tools.",
    "The goal of the ReAct framework is to combine reasoning and take actions.",
    "Reasoning refers to the model planning and executing actions based on observations from the environment.",
    "Actions are function calls or API calls by the model to retrieve additional information from external sources."
  ]
}